ps with large companies in need, empowering large corporate partners in multiple industries.\nFocus Areas\nOur Areas of Expertise\nEarly Stage Investment\nIn China, we have invested in over 100 hard-tech startups, among which 3 have grown into unicorns.\nbp@pnpchina.com\nportfolio@pnpchina.com\n![](https://www.plugandplaytechcenter.com/rendition/Office-Locations/APAC/China/China---Discussion.JPG)\nCorporate Innovation\nWe make corporate innovation easier by connecting large corporations with the brightest startups. Together, we help companies improve efficiency, reduce costs, explore new product lines, and drive innovation from their core.\nIn China, we have partnered with over 180 leading industry players, including Mercedes-Benz, Panasonic, Siemens, Sinotrans, and ANTA, to power open innovation tailored to their unique needs and ecosystems.\nToday, we drive innovation across 10+ industries, including Brand \u0026 Retail, Energy \u0026 Sustainability, Food \u0026 Biotech, Mobility, Supply Chain, Smart Cities, Fintech, and more.\nmarketing@pnpchina.com\n![](https://www.plugandplaytechcenter.com/rendition/Office-Locations/APAC/China/China---Partner-Logos.JPG)\nCity Innovation\nIn China, we work closely with municipal governments, high-tech parks, and local partners to build an international industrial innovation platform that integrates innovation services, startup investment, and co-working spaces. Our platform supports the transformation of traditional industries, nurtures enterprise growth, enables startups and global talent to thrive in China, and drives innovation across cities and industries.\nTo date, we have established six innovation centers and collaborated with more than 20 cities nationwide.\ncityinnovation@pnpchina.com\n![](https://www.plugandplaytechcenter.com/rendition/Office-Locations/APAC/China/China---Crowd-Photo.JPG)\nCross-Border Program\nThe Plug and Play Cross-Border Program is a platform that helps global startups enter the Chinese market and supports Chinese startups in expanding abroad.\nThrough cross-border innovation summits and curated introductions to global corporate partners, investors, local governments, and leading universities, we bridge China and the world in the field of innovation.\ninternational@pnpchina.com\n![](https://www.plugandplaytechcenter.com/rendition/Office-Locations/APAC/China/China---International-Hall.JPG)\nUniversity International Innovation\nAs a leading global platform for technological innovation, Plug and Play China plays a key role in accelerating business incubation, translating research results into real-world applications, driving equity investment, nurturing talent, and advancing internationalization.\nLeveraging this experience, we help our university partners build international sci-tech innovation and entrepreneurship networks, setting a benchmark for ecosystem development and global collaboration.\niie@pnpchina.com\n![](https://www.plugandplaytechcenter.com/rendition/Generic-Images/54179424930_fb65996520_k.jpg-medium.webp)\n![](https://www.plugandplaytechcenter.com/rendition/Office-Locations/APAC/China/China---PNP-China-Mic.jpg-full.webp)\nWhat's happening in China\nPlug and Play in China\nWalk into Plug and Play China\nPlug and Play China Innovation Milestone\nOur Chinese Offices\n![](https://www.plugandplaytechcenter.com/rendition/locations/APAC/Beijing/Beijing/hanson-lu-_8EFj6ISA08-unsplash.jpg-large.webp)\nBeijing\n![](https://www.plugandplaytechcenter.com/rendition/Office-Locations/APAC/China/Changzhou/pexels-khang-ocean-3810070-6403030.jpg-large.webp)\nChangzhou\n![](https://www.plugandplaytechcenter.com/rendition/Office-Locations/APAC/China/Hefei/Hefei---Square-Sky-Daytime-.jpg-large.webp)\nHefei\n![](https://www.plugandplaytechcenter.com/rendition/Office-Locations/APAC/China/Nantong/jeremy-huang-sbFQNgZEsek-unsplash.jpg-large.webp)\nNantong\n![](https://www.plugandplaytechcenter.com/rendition/locations/APAC/Shanghai/Shanghai/kin-li-e5IDfDCg-cE-unsplash.jpg